rows.label: tlk44200185_04_msg0001
rows.name:
Ahh, what I'd give to be able to read
a new novel...

rows.label: tlk44200185_04_msg0002
rows.name:
I think I've all but exhausted the
volumes that the Library Philosofia
has to offer.

rows.label: tlk44200185_04_msg0003
rows.name:
I heard there was once a girl who read
every last book in that place.

rows.label: tlk44200185_04_msg0004
rows.name:
Of course, I'm only interested in
prose. The purpler, the better!

rows.label: tlk44200185_04_msg0005
rows.name:
If only someone were around to give
me something new to read...

rows.label: tlk44200185_04_msg0007
rows.name:
I don't care about how recent the
story is. Just as long as it's something
that's not in the library!
